<h2 class="bold font-l">Wander "vs" Something So & So</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Sylvia tries to use a fight with Something the So-and-So to distract Wander from getting a love letter to Dominator, but he immediately snaps out of it. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="50cc5p" data-video-descrip="" data-video-title="Zoro Vs Mihawk" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/50cc5p_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/50cc5p.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/Eyedscreen" data-video-tropename="Eyedscreen" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Anime/OnePiece" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/50cc5p.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Zoro Vs Mihawk</span></p>
</a>
